org.jetel.data.xml.mapping

Class XMLElementMappingDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.data.xml.mapping.XMLMappingDefinition
      • org.jetel.data.xml.mapping.XMLElementMappingDefinition

  • public class XMLElementMappingDefinition
extends XMLMappingDefinition
    Represents a mapping from an XML structure to a clover record. Describes how a data (be it attributes, nested elements or text value) from given XML element are mapped to a fields of clover record.
